raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Player: Shower done 👌
Player: What are you up to?
if Story.has_flag(\"LOVE\") && Story.pink_heart >= 3:
	Mabel: 😊
	Mabel: Oh nothing at all Mr Smooches 😚
	Player: Is that what I am now? 😄
	Mabel: *nod* 🥰
	Player: 😊
	Mabel: Today's date was the best ever 😊
else:
	Mabel: Just checking what books I need for tomorrow
	Mabel: Today's date was so nice 😊
Mabel: Thanks for taking me out 🥰
Mabel: Can I share the pics you took on my phone? 🤩
Mabel: I just wanna cozy up to them hehe
Player: Of course!
if Story.has_flag(\"LOVE\"):
	Mabel: img: mabel/89
	Mabel: Here's me a little bit shy
	Mabel: Was the first time in a bikini like that, I'm usually more of a swimsuit girl hehe 🥰
	Player: Super cute!
	Mabel: Sorry it took me a while to get comfortable 🤭
	Mabel: Thought: My heart was racing like crazy
	Player: That's fine
Mabel: Oh!
Mabel: Here's me in the water!
Mabel: img: mabel/90
- That bikini is so cute
	Player: That bikini is so cute
	Mabel: I'm so glad it fit well
	Mabel: I didn't have time to try it on while packing 😵‍💫
- You're so beautiful [if Story.has_flag(\"NTS\")]
	Player: You're so beautiful
	Mabel: Gee why do you have to hit me with something like that 🙈
	Mabel: I'm glad you think so 🫠👉👈
Mabel: img: mabel/91
Player: You got my shirt wet!
Mabel: Babe we're in the ocean
Mabel: Why did you have your shirt on 😂
Player: To protect me from your splashes 😌
Mabel: If I knew that, I'd have splashed you more!! 😆
if Story.has_flag(\"NTR\"):
	do queue_social_post(\"mabel_beach_bikini\")
	Mabel: Thought: Oh here's THAT pic...
	Mabel: Thought: This is for the sorority..
	Mabel: Thought: Such an embarassing pose
	Mabel: Uhm... yeah anyway 👀
Player: img: mabel/93
Mabel: Whaaa!?
Mabel: When did you take that!!
Player: While you were laughing lol
Mabel: I know thaaat but omg I look so goofy!
Mabel: Delete it!! Can't let that leak to the public
Mabel: Agent007's rep is on the line 😭
Player: No way, it's too cute
Mabel: 🥹🩷
if Story.has_flag(\"LOVE\") && Story.pink_heart >= 3:
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: PinkThought: Oh my god, here it is
	Mabel: PinkThought: We look so cute, eep!
	Player: Do you have the last pic?
	Mabel: PinkThought: What do I say?? 
	Mabel: Uhh noo...
	Player: Mabel you definitely have it, why are you saying no 😂
	Mabel: OK I DO 😆 I'm just confused okay?
	Mabel: 🙈
	Mabel: It was our first kiss, it's been hard to act normal since then 🥰
	Mabel: img: mabel/94
	Mabel: 😊
	Mabel: It was... wet and soft and felt a bit silly but I loved it...
	Mabel: What about you?
	Mabel: Was it what you expected? Was I good at it? 👉👈
	- You were great
		Player: You were great
		Mabel: Awhh thanks babe 😚 Digital kisses!
		Mabel: You were all like Mlem mwah om nom
		Mabel: I think my nose was in your mouth at one point
		Player: Ok THAT didn't happen
		Mabel: Nehehe
		Mabel: Nice to tease you about something for a change 😁😘
	- We'll get better at it
		Player: We'll get better at it
		Mabel: Really, you want to do more? ☺️
		Mabel: I mean we kinda did a lot and got distracted but...
		Mabel: It felt like I could keep going hehe
		Mabel: Shame you live so far cause maybe we could come over and y'know...
		Mabel: Continue 🥰
		Player: Yeah, we'll find a way
	do heart(0)
Mabel: Jeez you really know how to show a girl a good time 🥰
if Story.has_flag(\"LOVE\"):
	Mabel: I wish I had experienced this side of you a little more back home
	Mabel: But I was a scaredy cat and believed in the cooties until like last year 😅😂
	Player: I remember you were wearing gloves the first time we held hands
	Mabel: Omg that was so long ago
	Mabel: PinkThought: You really remember that far back?
	Mabel: I need to go before I get all nostalgic already haha
	Mabel: I might cry if we keep chatting
	Mabel: Don't worry, it's just a girl thing... or maybe a me thing lol
	Player: Awwh okay! 
	Mabel: Love you!
	Player: Love you too!
else:
	Mabel: Talk to you soon babe
	Player: Talk soon
if Story.has_flag(\"NTR\") && Story.has_flag(\"mom3\"):
	set Story.flag = \"mom4\"
	set PhoneUnlocks.leak = \"mom4\"
=> END"
